          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are Cherokee Workwear Originals Ultra men's scrubs?",
            "content": "Cherokee Workwear Originals Ultra men's scrubs are a new line of high-performance healthcare workwear built for male nurses, LPNs, RNs, medical assistants, surgical techs, and other healthcare professionals who want advanced fabric technology and modern style at exceptional value. Ultra sets a new level of excellence in men's scrubs — engineered to exceed expectations and stand up to the toughest workdays. The men's lineup covers V-neck scrub tops, cargo jogger pants, straight leg cargo pants, a zip-front warm up jacket, and scrub sets, all available across a wide range of colors. All styles are New Arrivals."
          }
