        "item_8bk3if": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What fabric technology is used in Cherokee Workwear Originals Ultra men's scrubs?",
            "content": "Ultra introduces advanced fabric technology designed to keep you comfortable and confident throughout your shift. PROTX2® technology combats odors and sweat so you stay fresh from start to finish. The fabric is moisture-wicking with two-way stretch, drying quickly and allowing for unrestricted movement in every direction. Reinforced seams, elasticized cuffs, and triple-stitched shoulder panels add the durability to hold up through repeated washing and hard use."
