          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes Workwear Originals Ultra different from Workwear Originals?",
            "content": "Ultra upgrades the trusted Originals foundation with advanced fabric technology and modern silhouettes that standard <a href=\"https://www.cherokeeuniforms.com/workwear-originals-men-scrubs.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Workwear Originals </span></a>don't offer. The biggest difference is PROTX2® — an innovative technology that combats odors and sweat — plus moisture-wicking, two-way stretch fabric that dries quickly and moves with you. Ultra also introduces activewear-inspired silhouettes like cargo joggers and a zip-front warm up jacket, plus construction details like triple-stitched shoulder panels and elasticized cuffs. Same Cherokee reliability, raised to a higher standard."
